20 §292. Horsemen's Horse owners', trainers' and drivers' purse share
21 Amounts calculated as horsemen's horse owners', trainers' and drivers' purse share
22 under section 286 must be retained by the licensee to supplement purse money at the track
23 where the wager was placed, except that, for wagers placed at a racetrack in the State on a
24 simulcast race conducted at another racetrack in the State, 1.512% of the regular wagers
25 and 4.305% of the exotic wagers must be sent to the track in the State where the harness
26 race was conducted.
